statements: SELECT * FROM user_engagement_metrics;
SELECT user_id, engagement_score FROM user_engagement_metrics WHERE time_spent_seconds > 60;
SELECT MAX(engagement_score) AS max_score FROM user_engagement_metrics;
SELECT * FROM user_engagement_metrics ORDER BY session_date DESC;
SELECT AVG(engagement_score) AS avg_score FROM user_engagement_metrics WHERE module_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM user_engagement_metrics WHERE user_id = 1 AND engagement_score > 80 ORDER BY session_date DESC, time_spent_seconds ASC LIMIT 10;

SELECT user_id, module_id, AVG(engagement_score) AS avg_engagement FROM user_engagement_metrics WHERE session_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY user_id, module_id HAVING avg_engagement > 70 ORDER BY avg_engagement DESC;

SELECT user_id, SUM(time_spent_seconds) AS total_time_spent, COUNT(DISTINCT module_id) AS unique_modules FROM user_engagement_metrics WHERE session_date >= '2022-08-01' GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_time_spent > 3600 ORDER BY unique_modules ASC, total_time_spent DESC;

SELECT user_id, MAX(engagement_score) AS max_score, MIN(engagement_score) AS min_score, MAX(time_spent_seconds) AS max_time_spent FROM user_engagement_metrics WHERE module_id IN (1, 2, 3) GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY max_score DESC, min_score ASC;

SELECT user_id, module_id, session_date, engagement_score, time_spent_seconds FROM user_engagement_metrics WHERE user_id IN (3, 6, 9) AND session_date >= '2022-10-01' ORDER BY user_id ASC, module_id DESC, session_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM UserEngagementMetrics WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT engagement_type, engagement_value FROM UserEngagementMetrics WHERE engagement_type = 'Like' ORDER BY engagement_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, engagement_type, engagement_value FROM UserEngagementMetrics WHERE engagement_type IN ('View', 'Comment') ORDER BY engagement_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM ARTrainingModules WHERE module_id >= 100 ORDER BY module_name;
SELECT module_name, module_engagement_goal FROM ARTrainingModules WHERE module_engagement_goal = 'Advanced';
SELECT user_id, engagement_type, engagement_value, engagement_timestamp FROM UserEngagementMetrics WHERE user_id = 10 ORDER BY engagement_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM ARTrainingModules WHERE module_name = 'Introduction Module';
SELECT module_name, module_description FROM ARTrainingModules WHERE module_engagement_goal = 'High Engagement' ORDER BY module_id ASC;
SELECT SUM(engagement_value) AS total_engagement FROM UserEngagementMetrics;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_engagements FROM UserEngagementMetrics GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_engagements > 5;
SELECT * FROM UserMetrics WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT session_id, engagement_time FROM UserMetrics WHERE user_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM ARTrainingModules WHERE module_id = 3 ORDER BY module_name DESC;
SELECT module_name, module_description FROM ARTrainingModules WHERE release_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, module_id, completion_status FROM AnalysisResults WHERE user_id = 4 AND completion_status = TRUE;
SELECT user_id, engagement_time, interaction_count FROM UserMetrics ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM ARTrainingModules WHERE module_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT user_id, module_id, completion_status FROM AnalysisResults WHERE completion_status = true ORDER BY user_id, module_id;
SELECT user_id, engagement_time FROM UserMetrics WHERE engagement_time > 1000 AND interaction_count < 50;
SELECT * FROM ARTrainingModules WHERE release_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-06-30';
SELECT * FROM user_engagement_metrics;
SELECT user_id, engagement_score, session_duration FROM user_engagement_metrics WHERE session_duration > 60;
SELECT user_id, engagement_score FROM user_engagement_metrics ORDER BY engagement_score DESC;
SELECT module_id, module_name FROM ar_training_modules WHERE module_duration < 30;
SELECT user_id, progress_percent FROM ar_training_progress JOIN user_engagement_metrics ON ar_training_progress.user_id = user_engagement_metrics.user_id WHERE completion_status = TRUE;
SELECT user_id, engagement_score FROM user_engagement_metrics ORDER BY engagement_score DESC, user_id ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM ar_training_modules WHERE module_duration > 30 ORDER BY module_name ASC

SELECT user_id, feedback_text, rating FROM user_feedback WHERE rating >= 4 AND feedback_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY rating DESC
